name: json-spec
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "json-spec" %}
{% set version = "0.10.1" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/json-spec-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0b32fb0508d47115eccb4daa14731f101f1263fb57a8cb13ca49c960b05eb719

build:
  number: 0
  noarch:  python
  entry_points:
    - json = jsonspec.cli:main
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - jsonspec
    - jsonspec.misc
  commands:
    - pip check
    - json --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: http://py.errorist.io/json-spec
  summary: Implements JSON Schema, JSON Pointer and JSON Reference.
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - wolfv
